{"word":"Horn","slug":"horn","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Horn</b> Used to hold the anointing oil<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=1'>1Sa 16:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=39'>1Ki 1:39</a><br/> Used for a trumpet<br/> <a href='S:Trumpet'>Trumpet</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of divine protection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=3'>2Sa 22:3</a> <br/> - Of power<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=11'>1Ki 22:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=89&verse=24'>Psa 89:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=92&verse=10'>Psa 92:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=132&verse=17'>Psa 132:17</a> <br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=7&verse=24'>Dan 7:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=8&verse=9'>Dan 8:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=8&verse=20'>Dan 8:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=13'>Amo 6:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=4&verse=13'>Mic 4:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=35&chapter=3&verse=4'>Hab 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=1&verse=21'>Zec 1:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=5&verse=6'>Rev 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=12&verse=3'>Rev 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=13&verse=1'>Rev 13:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=13&verse=11'>Rev 13:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=17&verse=16'>Rev 17:16</a><br/><a href='S:Altar'>Altar</a>"}]}